# Language statistics (GitHub Linguist)
#
# This is a Python project: the LangChain RAG pipeline, the FastAPI service and
# the ticketing store are the substance of the repo. The React app in frontend/
# is a self-contained client for that API, and its TypeScript/CSS/HTML would
# otherwise outweigh the Python and be reported as the repo's main language.
#
# Marking it vendored excludes it from the language breakdown. The code is
# still tracked, diffed and reviewed as normal.
frontend/** linguist-vendored

# Build output and dependency lockfiles are machine-generated. (dist/ is
# gitignored today; the rule keeps the stats correct if that ever changes.)
frontend/dist/** linguist-generated
frontend/package-lock.json linguist-generated

# Prebuilt FAISS vector store — binary artifacts, not source.
faiss_index/** binary linguist-vendored
